</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>烏克蘭捕獲俄羅斯化石級無人機，單反放入土炮模型飛機，膠樽當做燃料缸 </title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/17/russiandroneisajoke/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=russiandroneisajoke</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 17 Apr 2022 02:57:58 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[俄羅斯]]></category><category><![CDATA[烏克蘭]]></category><category><![CDATA[無人機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1095546</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>烏克蘭軍方近日在 YouTube 上發佈影片，介紹捕獲到的俄羅斯無人機，而該無人機的製作技術極為落後，攝影零件 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">烏克蘭軍方近日在 YouTube 上發佈影片，介紹捕獲到的俄羅斯無人機，而該無人機的製作技術極為落後，攝影零件更是將整部 Canon EOS 單反相機直接放入無人機機身。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">被捕獲的無人機早於 2010 年由俄羅斯軍方發佈，型號為 Orlan-10 ，要價高達 12 萬美元（約港幣 94 萬元） 。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095548" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/drone-694x278.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="278" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/drone-694x278.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/drone-1280x512.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/drone-768x307.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/drone-1536x614.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/drone-2048x819.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/drone.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">影片展示一部被拆解的 Orlan-10，其體積較一般無人機龐大，外形與一般模型遙控飛機相似，使用螺旋槳引擎，只是外殼較堅固。機身燃料缸使用經加固的膠樽，入油時只需直接扭開樽蓋。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095549" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/tent-694x310.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="310" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/tent-694x310.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/tent-1280x572.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/tent-768x343.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/tent-1536x687.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/tent-2048x916.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/tent.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">攝影零件方面，Orlan-10 直接將整部 Canon EOS 單反相機放入無人機中，再連接商用紅外線熱能感應器。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095551" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera-694x379.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="379" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera-694x379.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera-1280x699.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera-768x420.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera-1536x839.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095550" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera2-694x444.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="444" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera2-694x444.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera2-1280x819.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera2-768x491.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/camera2.jpg 1510w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">此前，在 2014 年的克里米亞危急及敘利亞內戰中亦有見到這款無人機的蹤跡。在上月亦有一架 Orlan-10 在羅馬尼亞墜毀。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而影片中的烏克蘭軍人亦語帶諷刺地表示，在剛捕獲無人機時他們曾拍照傳送至北約，打算進行精密分析，但北約回覆這款無人機不可能有精密設計，讓烏克蘭自行處理即可。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Orlan-10 的設計簡陋，拍攝影像清晰度低。但由於俄羅斯軍方擁有大量裝備，無人機偵測到目標時仍可傳送影像，因此在行動途中若發現無人機，仍需撤離疏散，免受後續空襲。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_65120"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WP681BVWk0Q?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WP681BVWk0Q&amp;t=172s">YouTube</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
